How It Works
ThemeContext.Provider: Wraps the Toolbar component and provides the theme and toggleTheme function to all child components.

useContext Hook: Used in ThemedButton and ThemedText to access the context values (theme and toggleTheme).

Dynamic Updates: When the toggleTheme function is called, it updates the theme state, which triggers a re-render of all components consuming the context.